[1.0.0] - 2025-07-17
Added
Initial project setup with Streamlit framework

Basic app layout displaying cultural object images

User input functionality to enter slang/local names

Admin authentication using streamlit-authenticator

Data storage using Pandas CSV

Analytics dashboard with Plotly visualizations

Responsive glassmorphism UI design

Requirements.txt with all dependencies

Changed
Optimized image loading using Pillow for faster display

Improved UI layout with custom CSS for mobile responsiveness

Fixed
CSV file writing bug in user response storage

Admin login redirect issue on failed authentication

[0.1.0] - 2025-07-10
Added
Project idea finalized (Cultural Discovery Game)

Team roles and responsibilities assigned

Initial README.md created with problem statement, solution, and team details

Git repository initialized

